{"tid":2235773,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"葉國謙促讓大灣區港人投票 倡修改《選舉條例》重新定義「通常居港」","createTime":"2020-10-09T03:05:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-09T04:51:10.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"fd2699a096b533a037e371a13909790ccd30b26b","tid":2235773,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T03:05:33.000Z","msg":"有報道引述政府消息指，計劃在下屆立法會選舉，容許居住大灣區甚至在內地的港人投票。港區人大代表、民建聯葉國謙今早接受商台訪問時，指應修改《選舉條例》，重新定義「通常居港」的意思，讓境外的香港永久居民亦能投票。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201009/56SVJGJPGFDP3BEW2NQ5PZSHQE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201009%2F56SVJGJPGFDP3BEW2NQ5PZSHQE%2F&d=bW%2FimIc%2BBhL52Hx1BZusr8RCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=8f60c775\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201009%2F56SVJGJPGFDP3BEW2NQ5PZSHQE%2F&h=d878806f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201009/56SVJGJPGFDP3BEW2NQ5PZSHQE/</a>"},{"pid":"3e310e399053c62d3674673e17c132baaf8b1ec6","tid":2235773,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T03:07:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"65b9856953be4126c41928a3fdca4b43cbbc7339","tid":2235773,"uid":121197,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T03:08:13.000Z","msg":"改做通常居於中國咪得"},{"pid":"5aef113eef6c0bf6f1e945e353a5d0cb8ebce22d","tid":2235773,"uid":62721,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T03:08:53.000Z","msg":"咁要改名喎，不如叫中國立法會選舉？"},{"pid":"197ff216a0ddce1d9a2a25e54b187d6f07aad3cc","tid":2235773,"uid":34722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T03:12:05.000Z","msg":"通常居港 ＝ 通常不居住香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e24c5211aa2ff21aec83a4b85b812670af239b65","tid":2235773,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTim